(1605, 218, 'new_paragraph_4_new_content', '<a href="http://www.arc.ab.ca/" target="_blank">ARC</a>\r\nThe Alberta Research Council develops and commercializes technology for clients.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.innocentre.com/" target="_blank">Inno Centre</a>\r\nThe Alberta Inno Centre is involved in advising tech start-ups.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.avacltd.com/" target="_blank">AVAC</a>\r\nAVAC provides financial resources, knowledge, and coaching for Alberta''s value-added agricultural industry.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.canadabusiness.ab.ca/" target="_blank">The Business Link Business Services Centre\r\n</a>The Business Link Business Services Centre is a non-profit organization supported by the Government of Canada and the Government of Alberta that provides industry development grants, contributions, subsidies, incentives, shared-costs, and rebates.'),
