(2059, 277, '_new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(2060, 277, 'new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'Brownlee LLP''s Edmonton office offers an excellent opportunity for a Litigation Associate, with 3 to 5 years of experience, in our insurance department. You will have the ability to work in a vibrant insurance defense practice with a broad cross-section of talented litigators and a busy, client rich practice.\r\n\r\nOur firm offers an attractive compensation package including competitive salaries, great benefits, fitness reimbursement, parking allowance, etc.\r\n\r\nIf you believe that you would make a positive contribution to our Litigation team, please submit your application materials in confidence to:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBrownlee LLP\r\n2200, 10155 – 102 Street\r\nEdmonton, AB T5J 4G8\r\nAttn: Ryan Ewasiuk\r\nFax: 780-424-3254\r\nE-mail: <a href="mailto:rewasiuk@brownleelaw.com">rewasiuk@brownleelaw.com</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>*Please note only successful candidates will be contacted. All resumes received will be kept on file for a period of 6 months at which time they will be destroyed. All information provided to us is for the purpose of obtaining employment with our firm.</em>'),
