(2571, 70, 'representative_work', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Has represented multiple insurers and clients in pursuing and recovering on subrogated claims including fire losses, damages to tanker trailers, environmental clean-up costs, construction losses, losses arising from defective products, business downtime losses and motor vehicle damages;</li>\r\n	<li>Defence counsel for international fabrication company involving $20 million dollar products liability claim for allegedly defective part installed in a gas plant destroyed by fire;</li>\r\n	<li>Defence counsel for international insurer regarding $15 million products liability claim for destruction by fire of an oil rig in Alberta;</li>\r\n	<li>Defence counsel in numerous serious injury and fatality claims;</li>\r\n	<li>Defence of pharmacies and pharmacists on allegations of negligent dispensing errors causing bodily injury and fatality;</li>\r\n	<li>Defence counsel for multiple multinational retailers and national property managers on occupier''s liability and commercial GL claims;</li>\r\n	<li>Defence of insurers on disability and bad faith claims;</li>\r\n	<li>Defence of employers on wrongful dismissal claims;</li>\r\n	<li>Defence of a software developer for performance related issues;</li>\r\n	<li>Defence of product liability and negligence claims involving ladders, elevators, water heaters, oil rigs, elevators, gas plants and various construction projects;</li>\r\n	<li>Represented multiple contractors in construction litigation to recover damages against a general contractor on a large multi-family residential construction project;</li>\r\n	<li>Defence counsel for professional sued for breach of fiduciary duty in a medical setting;</li>\r\n	<li>Defence of various claims involving allegedly negligent seismic testing activities related to the oil industry;</li>\r\n	<li>Numerous contractual disputes, including construction, shareholder disputes, intellectual property, performance, and default issues;</li>\r\n	<li>Coverage counsel in several motor vehicle and construction related matters;</li>\r\n	<li>Counsel for directors and business owners engaged in various contractual and shareholder dispute related issues;</li>\r\n	<li>Defence counsel in respect of multiple toxic mold and construction deficiency claims;</li>\r\n	<li>Defence counsel for corporations in numerous claims involving server-host liability; and</li>\r\n	<li>Coverage and defence counsel in numerous and varied other construction deficiency, property and products liability losses involving commercial and public facilities.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
