(4162, 372, 'bio', 'Aaron was called to the Bar in Ontario in 2004 and Alberta in 2010.  He practices in Brownlee LLP''s insurance defence litigation group.\r\n\r\nAaron articled at a prominent insurance defence firm in Toronto before commencing a broad litigation practice in Ontario and Alberta.  He has extensive litigation experience, which includes insurance defence, professional liability, commercial litigation, construction litigation; and, construction lien (Ontario) and builder''s lien (Alberta) actions.\r\n\r\nAaron has conducted trials before the Alberta Court of Queen''s Bench, Ontario''s Superior Court of Justice and the Ontario Court of Justice. He has also appeared as counsel at hearings, motions, and applications before the referenced courts as well as the Ontario Court of Appeal and the Alcohol and Gaming Commission of Ontario''s Licence Appeal Tribunal.'),
