(485, 1, '2014-03-16 06:58:34', '2014-03-16 06:58:34', '', 'BROWNLEE SPONSORS SLGM AWARD OF EXCELLENCE', 'Brownlee LLP is again sponsoring the Society of Local Government Managers (SLGM) Award of Excellence.\r\nPartner, Paul V. Stocco will be presenting the Award of Excellence at the awards banquet being held on May 10th. The Award of Excellence was initiated to recognize individuals who demonstrate service excellence in local government. The award is distributed annually and is open to any regular associate or student member of the SLGM. Additionally, Paul will be presenting "Construction and Tendering - Do''s and Don''ts" on Thursday, May 10th 2012, from 9:00AM to 12:00Noon, and Steven T-Connors, partner and the firm’s litigation practice area leader, will be presenting from 1:30PM to 4:30PM on "Sick and Disabled Employees: The Cure for What Ails You.”  The Society of Local Government Managers spans the Province of Alberta and fosters learning through its educational events, workshops, meetings, publications, and mentoring programs. Brownlee LLP is proud to be contributing to the growth of improved local governance. Interested parties can view the event PDF here.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'brownlee-sponsors-slgm-award-of-excellence', '', '', '2014-03-16 06:58:34', '2014-03-16 06:58:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost/brownlee/?post_type=news&#038;p=485', 0, 'news', '', 0),
